194
00:20:21,140 --> 00:20:22,610
Tak disangka berubah
jadi manusia.

195
00:20:22,610 --> 00:20:23,610
Perubahan.

196
00:20:23,770 --> 00:20:25,140
Manusia yang licik.

197
00:20:25,310 --> 00:20:26,570
Kubunuh kau!

198
00:20:26,740 --> 00:20:27,410
Hati-hati!

199
00:20:27,940 --> 00:20:30,210
Ada apa ini? Bukankah
ia tak akan melukai kita?

200
00:20:40,140 --> 00:20:43,170
Yang Mulia Pemimpin Suci tiba.

201
